Text: Contact infoResumeSteve I am not sure if you remember meeting me when you were in India several months back but I am a manager with Global Finance dedicated to the India team I received the following resume from a very good old friend of mine and thought you might be able to channel it in the right direction I only have very positive things to say about Bill I hope you find that his skills and backgrounds are of use to Enron and consider talking to him I am in India now but am available should you have any questions him Thank you for your consideration am Forwarded by Andrea MillerENRONDEVELOPMENT on AM William Maguire on PM To cc Subject Contact infoResume Hey Andrea I spent some time exploring Enrons website and am very intrigued by your companys extensive philanthropic programs and would be very interested in speaking with anyone you might think would be appropriate Ive attached my resume just in case Of course absolutely no pressure on you Any chance that youll be in the bay area anytime soon Cheers Bill williammaguireresumedoc
